\nw[Dalton]It's getting dark already. According to the map,
we should be just a little further to the cabin...

\nw[Nonna]I'm just used to the forest. Look, it's right in
front of us now.

\nw[Dalton]Oh, well then. Looks like we'll be staying here
overnight.

\nw[Dalton]Well then, now that we've finished eating, let's
do what we need to do and take a rest.

\nw[Dalton]Of course it's sex. It's only natural when there
are a man and a woman alone together.

\nw[Nonna]Dalton, you're quite energetic for your age.
Aren't you starting to feel reluctant about sexual
activities?

\nw[Dalton]If that's the case, I'll never quit being a
mercenary. I intend to be active in both battles
and sex for my whole life.

\nw[Dalton]Alright, if you understand, let's get started.
Nonna, it's fine for you to be embraced by someone
other than your lover, right?

\nw[Nonna]Yes, I wanted to send magical power to Prae too.
I'm not used to this kind of act, so I would
appreciate it if you could teach me.

\nw[Dalton]Ah, leave it to me. I've been doing this for over
30 years, so I'll make sure it feels good.

\nw[Dalton]Well then, now that we've finished eating, let's
do what we need to do today and take a rest.
\nw[Dalton]Hmmm, as expected, you seem to understand.

\nw[Nonna]It's been a while since I joined this mercenary
group.

\nw[Nonna]Come on, let's start early. We have tomorrow too,
so time is precious.
